HEADWORD: Collectivism
<hw>Col*lect"iv*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>collectivisme</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Polit. Econ.)</fld> <def>The
doctrine that land and capital should be owned by society collectively
or as a whole; communism.</def> <rj><au>W. G. Summer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
